OL,3,CSuncream, frozen toys and shade: How
OL,4,Cto keep pets safe in the heat
OL,6,FAs the UK is braced for record-
OL,7,Fbreaking temperatures this week, it's
OL,8,Fnot only people who will be feeling
OL,9,Fthe heat.
OL,11,FPets can also experience sunburn and
OL,12,Fheatstroke, so it's important to take
OL,13,Fthe right measures to keep them cool.
OL,15,FHere, ITV News explains how to protect
OL,16,Fyour pets during the heatwave.
OL,18,FShade and water
OL,20,FPets should have constant access to
OL,21,Fshaded areas, inside and outside.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
