OL,3,CSuncream, frozen toys and shade: How
OL,4,Cto keep pets safe in the heat
OL,6,FPet-safe suncream can help prevent
OL,7,Fsunburn on your pet's skin, like their
OL,8,Fears and nose.
OL,10,FThis is particularly important for
OL,11,Fpets with white or light-coloured fur,
OL,12,Fas they "can be very vulnerable to
OL,13,Fgetting burned", according to the
OL,14,FRSCPA.
OL,16,FFrozen toys and paddling pools
OL,18,FFor dogs, frozen toys and paddling
OL,19,Fpools can help keep them entertained
OL,20,Fand cool them down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
