OL,3,CSuncream, frozen toys and shade: How
OL,4,Cto keep pets safe in the heat
OL,6,FYou can also give them a damp towel to
OL,7,Flie on or an ice pack wrapped in a
OL,8,Ftowel.
OL,10,FHowever, the RSPCA warns against
OL,11,Fputting a damp towel over them, as it
OL,12,Fcan trap in the heat.
OL,14,FFor cats, you can freeze a bottle of
OL,15,Fwater, wrap it in a towel or
OL,16,Fpillowcase and place it somewhere your
OL,17,Fcat goes regularly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
